Business Analyst Buy Side (Asset Management, BA, change project
Business Analyst Buy Side (Asset Management, BA, change project
Location:  --Abu Dhabi
Salary:  GBP620 - GBP700 per day + expensesBusiness Analyst Buy Side (Investment Management, Business Analysis, Project Management, Buy Side, Asset Management, Delivery, Programmes, Charles River, stakeholder management, change programmes)
Global consultancy is looking for a Business Analyst to work on the delivery of of Charles River and other Investment / Asset Management solutions for their client onsite at their Head Office in Abu Dhabi.
The Business Analyst will be responsible for the analysis and delivery of multiple, business critical projects, for investment & asset management solutions within the business. The Business Analyst will be involved in the stakeholder management, analysis, documentation, understanding requirements, resource allocation, workshops and getting the projects completed on time and to budget.
The suitable candidate MUST have come from a proven Business Analysis background delivering Investment Management, Asset Management or Buy Side solutions for clients. In depth knowledge of Investment Management, Project Management, Buy Side, Asset Management, Delivery, Programmes, Charles River, Latent Zero, stakeholder management is key. Excellent interpersonal and communication skills are essential.
